{"search_data": "Himachal PradeshHimachal Pradesh Mukhyamantri Nirog Yojana \u2013 Free Health Check-Up & Medicines Himachal Pradesh cabinet launches Mukhyamantri Nirog Yojana in the state to provide free health check-ups & medicines to all citizens for early identification and treatment of diseases, no age bar and is applicable to all permanent residents of the state \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902HP Mukhyamantri Nirog Yojana for All CitizensThe important features and highlights of CM Nirog Yojana are as follows:-All the citizens of the state belonging to any age group can avail the scheme benefits.The state govt. will provide free medicines to the citizens for all types of diseases.Mukhyamantri Nirog Yojana will primarily benefit the poor people so that they can get proper treatment on time. Health problems can be identified at the initial stage to provide proper treatment to the people.Under this scheme, random blood tests, eye check-up, blood pressure test and other tests would be performed absolutely free of cost.In the initial phase, the state govt. will provide 330 free medicines while 66 medicines are already available.All the children below 8 years of age will get free injections for insulin and haemophilia.This scheme will reduce the risk of Measles and Rubella.The state govt. of Himachal Pradesh has launched Mukhyamantri Nirog Yojana in order to perform general health check up of the people. This scheme is to be implemented by the health department of the state.Random tests for blood sugar, blood pressure, eye check-up and other lab check-ups will be performed. These tests will help in the identification of long term problems of the citizens.\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u093f\u092e\u0902\u0921\u0932 \u0915\u0940 \u092c\u0948\u0920\u0915 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0905\u0939\u092e \u0935\u093f\u0937\u092f\u094b\u0902 \u092a\u0930 \u091a\u0930\u094d\u091a\u093e \u0915\u0930\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u093e\u